{"tid":1120062,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[圖海] TWICE回歸太火辣 子瑜大腿全都露","createTime":"2019-04-22T11:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T10:51:59.000Z","uid":74065,"like":25,"dislike":125,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"50908850d02e7f9978af25fae97a37a22bd3be10","tid":1120062,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8T3wV1E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8T3wV1E.jpg&h=9328a57e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2019-04-22 16:18聯合報 記者李姿瑩╱即時報導<br />\n<br />\n 韓國女團TWICE今天在首爾舉辦回歸Showcase，為迷你七輯「FANCY YOU」宣傳。她們這次 走性感風，所有成員都穿上黑色緊身型服，因為裙子太短，一跳舞就露出安全褲，搭配上 性感表情，和過去清純甜美模樣差距甚大。<br />\n<br />\n她們嘗試轉型，妝容也變得更加艷麗，多數粉絲都感到不習慣，但還是讚嘆偶像美貌，希 望這次回歸能夠再造佳績。韓國媒體也拍攝了海量她們的表演照片，讚嘆子瑜是「連攝影 機都驚嘆的美貌」。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oNTVp5Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoNTVp5Z.png&h=83c7d84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE新歌走性感風。圖/摘自NEWS1<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WMoJg9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWMoJg9a.jpg&h=e1a904b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMOMO挑戰微露事業線。圖/摘自TVReport<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0YYB83o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0YYB83o.jpg&h=f56bdada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n娜璉一轉身就露出安全褲。圖/摘自NEWS1<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MkOYhny.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMkOYhny.jpg&h=21f452f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE新歌走性感風。圖/摘自OSEN"},{"pid":"2ae482ae121c730b7db1c9edd6c01aeb18daa990","tid":1120062,"uid":143093,"like":243,"dislike":10,"score":233,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"造型雞味濃到"},{"pid":"1ddd2d10e3b3f37b36b546507a89c2051823c057","tid":1120062,"uid":152123,"like":178,"dislike":3,"score":175,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"呢張圖好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\"